description.en:
During the course deals with the following topics:
- the meaning and criteria of professionalism;
- professional attitude and identity;
- professional guidance, reflecting it;
- professional ethics of teacher and youth worker;
- quality in youth work, evaluation of it.

description.et:
Noorsootöö professionaliseerumine
professionaalsuse käsitusi;
professionalism noorsootöös.

Noorsootöötaja kutse:
noorsootöötaja pädevus ja kompetentsid;
ametite paljusus noorsootöötaja kutse raames.
